        "main_text": "<p>Here at Crafter’s Companion, we’re committed to <strong>supporting our local community <\/strong>in the North East of England, as well as across the world. We’re proud to support a number of different charities with various fundraising<strong> activities <\/strong>throughout the year – <strong>take a peek at<\/strong> what we’ve been up to!<\/p>",
